text: Gnathoenia venerea is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1858. It is known from Cameroon, the Central African Republic, Angola, Gabon, and the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Gnathoenia venerea.
